---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Join Arc^ Initiative" description="Connect with Arc^ Initiative: Discord, contact form, email, and upcoming onboarding journeys for plasma-activated water research.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-20">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-muted">Join the initiative</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-semibold">Let’s explore plasma futures together</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-muted">
      Whether you’re a student pitching a thesis, a community lab coordinator, or an independent builder, we’d love to hear how Arc^ can support your research. The links below are placeholders while we set up the right infrastructure—check back as we grow.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pb-16" id="discord">
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Discord (coming soon)</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
        We’re preparing a moderated Discord space where project teams coordinate builds, share risk updates, and host office hours. Until the invite link is ready, leave your interest in the contact form below.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pb-16" id="contact">
    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Contact form (under construction)</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
          We’re building a form that lets you specify your discipline, interest area, and desired commitment so we can route you to the right collaborator track.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-sm text-muted">
          <li>Students can request a supervisor info pack.</li>
          <li>Community labs can express interest in hosting prototypes.</li>
          <li>Researchers can propose sub-studies or data collaborations.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-arkup-teal/30 bg-arkup-teal/10 p-6 text-sm text-muted">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Need to reach us now?</h3>
        <p class="mt-3">
          Email <a class="font-semibold text-white" href="mailto:writingsbyali@gmail.com">writingsbyali@gmail.com</a> with a short intro, the project idea you’re considering, and any deadlines you’re working to.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em]">Response window: within five working days</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 pb-20" id="youtube">
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">YouTube knowledge base (planned)</h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
        Expect deep dives on plasma basics, ethical framing, and build walkthroughs. We’ll launch with foundational explainers so supervisors and community members can align quickly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
